<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />日式年節料理當中的每一種食材，<delay8 />
似乎都有獨特的意義喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如說<delay8 />昆布就跟喜悅的日文發音類似，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而魚板因為形狀類似朝陽，<delay20 />
所以也相當吉利！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你喜歡<delay8 />哪種啊？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比起年節料理，
更喜歡拉麵喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要收到充滿心意的賀年卡，<delay20 />
心情就會變得很好呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每年的年底<delay8 />我老是忙得不可開交，<delay20 />
最後都來不及寄賀年卡。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒關係，<delay20 />明年一定會寄的啦！<delay20 /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><size value="75" />大概……<size value="100" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀～<delay8 />還真是不可思議啊。<delay frames="40" />
說起來，<delay8 />跟昨天相比，<delay20 />
不管你、我，或是這座島都沒什麼變化。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過光是迎接新年，<delay20 />
就有種一切都煥然一新的感覺！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想好新年新希望了嗎？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的話……<delay8 />每年都一樣喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />超越去年的自己！！<delay frames="40" />
很帥吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊，<delay8 />
在很久以前的新年寫了毛筆字，<delay20 />
結果大家看了都讚嘆不已。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所有人都說<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「這蛇畫得真好！」<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />實在是很沒禮貌啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>